{{zh-forms|[[男儿膝下有黄金]]|[[男兒]][[膝下]][[有]][[黃金]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: nán'ér xīxià yŏu huángjīn
===Etymology===
Literally: There is gold under a man's knees (so why kneel down?).
===Proverb===
# A man should have dignity and not grovel or bow down.
